1.dialouge: I've got to say, it's nice seeing some familiar faces here.

3.dialouge: I'd say I'm hard at work, accept that's lie.

4.dialouge: The captain took one good look at me and instantly knew that I didn't stack up to the rest.

5.dialouge: He halved my shard quota on the spot!

6.dialouge: I would have appreciated that, if everything didn't start laughing at me.
